# Bundled Freemius SDK - third-party vendored code.
# Do not normalise line endings, do not apply our coding-standard reformatting,
# and treat as vendored (collapsed in diffs, excluded from language stats).
# The SDK ships with CRLF line endings; -text preserves them byte-for-byte so
# tooling never rewrites these files.
src/freemius/** -text linguist-vendored
src/freemius/** -diff
